, technologique ou urbanistique du pays, il fut également, on le sait moins, pionnier en matière de politique environnementale. Nos archives en témoignent. L'occasion d'éclairer ce pan méconnu de son engagement politique avec l'historien Olivier Sibre, directeur des études et de la recherche à l'Institut Georges Pompidou.</div>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      \n      \n      </div>\n\n\n\n      <div class=\"mt-5\" id=\"hitsProgression\">\n    <div class=\"text-center\" style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600\"><span class=\"_count\">1</span>\n      contenus\n      sur 2</div>\n    <div class=\"progress mt-2 divCenter\" style=\"width: 180px; height: 4px\">\n      <div class=\"progress-bar\" role=\"progressbar\"\n           style=\"width: 50%; height: 4px; background: #000\"\n           aria-valuenow=\"1\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"2\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n      <div class=\"btn-n2 mt-5 mb-5 divCenter\">\n      <button class=\"btn-hub plusHits\">\n        <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n          <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"\n                d=\"M16.75 8.1001H9.5V0.850098C9.5 0.436098 9.164 0.100098 8.75 0.100098C8.336 0.100098 8 0.436098 8 0.850098V8.1001H0.75C0.336 8.1001 0 8.4361 0 8.8501C0 9.2641 0.336 9.6001 0.75 9.6001H8V16.8501C8 17.2641 8.336 17.6001 8.75 17.6001C9.164 17.6001 9.5 17.2641 9.5 16.8501V9.6001H16.75C17.164 9.6001 17.5 9.2641 17.5 8.8501C17.5 8.4361 17.164 8.1001 16.75 8.1001Z\"\n                fill=\"white\"></path>\n        </svg>\n        <span class=\"libelle\">Afficher plus de résultats</span>\n      </button>\n      <span class=\"alert-danger\" id=\"error\"></span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"mt-5\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n\n  \n<script>\n  const search_hits = {\n    q: \"rust\",\n    sort: \"_score\",\n    order: \"desc\",\n    espace: \"L&#039;INA éclaire l&#039;actu\",\n    media: \"Articles\",\n    categorie: \"\"\n  }